                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4175111/">L O M</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一颗星给封面 内容只值两颗星</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
